deck: A comic creator and a teacher.
description:
Karasik was born in the year 1956.

He hasn`t done many comic novels. But he has worked as an art teacher, made gag comics for New Yorker and collected all comics of Fletcher Hanks in to two separate books (first one of these has a short comic by him).

He collaborated with his sister, Judy, on a prose novel that had comic sections, called The Ride Together.
name: Paul Karasik
